--Composite columns
--composite columns allow columns to be grouped together with braces so they are treated as a single unit when determinging the necessary groupings

--ROLLUP((a,b),c) --2+1=3
--(a,b,c)
--(a,b)
--()

--CUBE((a,b),c)
--(a,b,c)
